{"lemma":"غِيلَة","slug":"غِيلَة","root":"غ.#.ل","root_slug":"غ-_-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-_-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32657","n32770","n32769"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"murder by stealth or deceit; assassination","examples":[{"text":"قَتَلَهُ غِيلَةً","english":"He killed him by stealth."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"harm caused to a child when its mother breastfeeds while pregnant","tags":["figuratively"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣiː.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32657","headword_ar":"غِيلَةٌ","root":"gwl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slaying covertly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on an occasion of inadvertence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AigotaAlahu","text_ar":"اِغْتَالَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb:) originally with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giwolapN","text_ar":"غِوْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) See 8: and see also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gyl","text_ar":"غيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n32770","headword_ar":"غِيلَةٌ","root":"gyl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayolN","text_ar":"غَيْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same; (Mgh, O, Msb); i. e. The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compressing one's wife while she is suckling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb:) thus expl. by AO as stated by A'Obeyd: (Mgh:) and thus the former signifies accord. to El-'Alkamee; and so says Málik: or, accord. to El-Munáwee, it signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"compressing one's wife while she is suckling"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pregnant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, accord. to ISk, a woman's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suckling while pregnant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(from a marginal note in a copy of the Jámi' es-Sagheer of Es-Suyootee, in explanation of a trad. mentioned in what here follows, commencing with the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqado hamamotu","text_ar":"لَقَدْ هَمَمْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayolN","text_ar":"غَيْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has this last signification (Mgh, TA) accord. to Ks: (Mgh:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giylapN","text_ar":"غِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aisotagoyalato","text_ar":"اِسْتَغْيَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and IAth says that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayolapN","text_ar":"غَيْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. thereof; or, as some say, this denotes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single act"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giylap","text_ar":"غِيلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; or the pronunciation with fet-h is not allowable unless with the elision of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDar~ati Algiylapu biwaladi fulaAnK","text_ar":"اَضَرَّتِ الغِيلَةُ بِوَلَدِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His mother's being compressed while she was suckling him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injured the child of such a one"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and likewise"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his mother's being pregnant while she was suckling him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) [But] in a trad. is related the saying, (of the Prophet, O) “ Verily I had intended to forbid"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Algiylap","text_ar":"الغِيلَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, * O, Msb, K) until I remembered that the Persians and the Greeks practise it and it does not injure their children. ” (Mgh, O, Msb.) [See also 4 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fsd","text_ar":"فسد"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of deceiving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beguiling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AigotiyaAlN","text_ar":"اِغْتِيَالٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, K: [see 8, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giylapN","text_ar":"غِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as expl. in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gwl","text_ar":"غول"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) accord. to Aboo-Bekr, in the language of the Arabs it signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causing evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slaughter, to come"},{"kind":"text","text":"to another"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from an unknown quarter."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qatalahu giylapF","text_ar":"قَتَلَهُ غِيلَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He deceived,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beguiled, him, and went with him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took him, to a place, and slew him"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he reached it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he slew him at unawares."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Abu-l- 'Abbás, TA.)       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aqo$iqap","text_ar":"شَقْشِقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"faucial bag of the he-camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IAar, K.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","O","Msb","TA","K","S"]},{"entry_id":"n32769","headword_ar":"غَيْلَةٌ","root":"gyl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giylapN","text_ar":"غِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also A single act of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AigotiyaAl","text_ar":"اِغْتِيَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giylapN","text_ar":"غِيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giylN","text_ar":"غِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A3-  It is also fem. of the epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayolN","text_ar":"غَيْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}